Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.26,0:22:55.74,EDC,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}一定是这样  当数不清的愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.26,0:23:00.74,EDC,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}全部如愿之后
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.16,0:23:05.84,EDC,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}我们还会贪婪地没有休止
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.09,0:23:10.12,EDC,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}直到开始后悔
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.25,0:23:12.77,EDC,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}永远过不够的昨天
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.77,0:23:15.16,EDC,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}和不断积蓄的回忆
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.16,0:23:20.88,EDC,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}就这样重叠着伴我前行
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.20,0:23:27.09,EDC,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}能够成为非常喜欢的人的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.18,0:23:32.16,EDC,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}非常喜欢的人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.26,0:23:37.32,EDC,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}连这样的奇迹
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.46,0:23:42.06,EDC,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}我还无法完全相信
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.06,0:23:46.76,EDC,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}总是难以如愿
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.92,0:23:52.48,EDC,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}多想再长高一些
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.54,0:23:54.86,EDC,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}愿我可以笑着
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.93,0:23:57.34,EDC,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}用幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.41,0:24:00.58,EDC,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}为明天
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.18,0:24:05.32,EDC,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}命名
